u_{\text{A}}-u_{\text{B}}=\frac{2a_{\text{B}}}{\gamma-1}\left[\left(\frac{p_{\text{A}}}{p_{\text{B}}}\right)^{\frac{\gamma-1}{2\gamma}}-1\right]\cdot\begin{cases}
-1 & \lambda_{1}\\
+1 & \lambda_{3}
\end{cases}\label{eq:速度差_膨胀波}
